General.Name: Econframe Bhd
General.Description: Econframe Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells doors, and door and window frames in Malaysia. It operates through Manufacturing and Trading segments. The company offers metal and wooden doors and frames, fire resistant door sets, steel doors, and pre-hung doors. It is also involved in the trading of wooden doors; and ironmongery, such as handles, locks, closing devices, and accessories, as well as trading and provision of installation services for solar energy products and systems. In addition, the company trades in electronics and electrical systems and accessories. It offers its products under the ECONFRAME and DUROE brands. The company serves contractors and building materials trading arms of property developers. Econframe Berhad was founded in 2001 and is based in Klang, Malaysia.
